missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: There are many wounded following the recent evacuation of our base at Briggia. Red Squadron's X-Wings are to maintain area security while the wounded are brought to the Alliance Medical Frigate Redemption. The Corvette Korolev is bringing in most of the wounded and several transports will deliver the rest. Stay alert for any Imperial marauders. The Empire has already dealt us a serious blow!
The first medical transport has arrived.
The second medical transport has arrived.
The Korolev is exiting hyperspace. Guide her in.
An Imperial Frigate is jumping in. It's the Harasser.
The Harasser is launching fighters. Keep them off the Korolev!
The Harasser is leaving the system.
Another Imperial Frigate is jumping in. It's the Warspite.
The Warspite is launching fighters. Keep them off the medical transports.
The Warspite is leaving the system.
There are still Imperial fighters active. Destroy them!
Well done Red Squadron. We'll see you at the rendezvous. Redemption out.
We can't stay here long. The Empire has almost certainly tracked us.
Okay Red Squadron. Head to the jump point.

missionEventData.data3: Pilots, all I can do is say thank you, those Nebulon Type Twos could have inflicted some serious damage, but you held them at bay saving the lives of hundreds of soldiers. Now, get some rest, Rebel Command has something different planned for our next mission
